OL,3,CPolice hold public meeting after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FA public meeting has been organised to
OL,7,Fallow people to "speak openly"
OL,8,Ffollowing a fatal stabbing in Market
OL,9,FRasen.
OL,11,FDanny Fowler, 37, was found with stab
OL,12,Fwounds on Union Street on the evening
OL,13,Fof Thursday 12 March. He died in
OL,14,Fhospital.
OL,16,FThree people were due to appear in
OL,17,Fcourt on Monday charged with murder.
OL,19,FPolice have organised a public meeting
OL,20,Fon Monday to allow residents to
OL,21,Fdiscuss concerns.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
