OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773765948
OL,3,CPolice hold public meeting after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FInsp Michael Head said in a social
OL,7,Fmedia post: "I am aware that recent
OL,8,Fevents have caused concern among
OL,9,Fresidents in Market Rasen, and I want
OL,10,Fto ensure that the community has the
OL,11,Fopportunity to speak openly about any
OL,12,Fissues they may be experiencing or
OL,13,Fworries they wish to raise."
OL,15,FThe meeting, at The Festival Hall, was
OL,16,Forganised to "hear directly from
OL,17,Fresidents, understand the challenges
OL,18,Fyou are facing, and ensure that your
OL,19,Fviews and concerns are acknowledged",
OL,20,Fthe inspector said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
