OL,3,CPolice hold public meeting after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FOn Monday Ryan Townhill, 29, of no
OL,7,Ffixed address, Martin Doocey, 55, of
OL,8,FWaverley Court, and Shannon Doocey,
OL,9,F31, of Mill Street, were due to appear
OL,10,Fat Lincoln Magistrates' Court charged
OL,11,Fwith murder and weapons offences.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
